about Christmasland.

07:30.576 --> 07:32.370
Miserable harpies.

07:51.055 --> 07:52.598
Hold on!

07:52.723 --> 07:54.058
[ Tires screech ]

07:54.183 --> 07:56.352
MAGGIE:
What are you doing?

07:56.477 --> 07:57.478
VIC:
We leave this Bridge,

07:57.603 --> 07:59.605
he follows us
straight to the people we love.

07:59.730 --> 08:01.607
