08:01.732 --> 08:05.277
He's nothing in here.
Just an old bitch like you said.

08:10.491 --> 08:12.118
[ Wheezing ]

08:17.081 --> 08:18.874
MAGGIE:
Listen to me, Brat.

08:19.000 --> 08:21.002
My Tiles chose you
because you are brave

08:21.127 --> 08:22.128
