08:22.253 --> 08:23.629
My Tiles are never wrong.

08:28.217 --> 08:30.094
[ Engine revs]

08:34.597 --> 08:36.267
<i>CHARLIE: [Echoing]
<i>Our lnscapes are manifestations</i></i>

08:36.392 --> 08:38.184
<i>of our minds.</i>

08:38.309 --> 08:41.272
<i>The Shorter Way was impressive
as advertised.</i>

08:41.397 --> 08:42.481
[ Bats chittering ]

08:42.606 --> 08:44.692
<i>WAYNE:
Look at all the bats!</i>

08:44.817 --> 08:47.570
<i>CHARLIE: You'll want to
