10:41.058 --> 10:43.102
We gotta get out of here.

10:48.190 --> 10:50.860
Vic, we gotta
haul ass right now!

11:13.174 --> 11:15.009
Mom?

11:16.677 --> 11:17.720
Morn.

11:19.180 --> 11:21.557
Are you okay?

11:23.976 --> 11:25.436
TABITHA:
Special Agent Tabitha Hutter

11:25.561 --> 11:29.315
requesting an ambulance
at 225 Pleasant Street.

11:29.440 --> 11:31.483
I have one dead,
two critically wounded.

11:31.609 --> 11:32.776
This is an emergency.

11:32.902 --> 11:34.486
<i>MAN:
Copy that, Agent Hutter.</i>

11:39.325 --> 11:42.536
He's -- He's dead, Lou.

11:44.538 --> 11:46.874
