12:08.687 --> 12:10.356
Someone's here.

12:16.195 --> 12:17.529
Whoa.

12:17.655 --> 12:19.615
Where's Father Christmas?

12:22.159 --> 12:23.577
Dad?

12:24.912 --> 12:27.039
