You gotta eat something.

14:00.966 --> 14:03.010
- No, it's gross.
- Wayne, this is --

14:05.387 --> 14:06.597
LOU:
It's alright.

14:11.352 --> 14:12.728
You'll eat when you're ready.

14:12.853 --> 14:14.313
Go and clear your plate.

14:33.540 --> 14:36.126
It's just a couple tater tots.

14:36.251 --> 14:38.587
He hasn't eaten a normal meal
in weeks.

14:38.712 --> 14:41.465
How long did it take you
to get over Charlie Manx?

14:44.510 --> 14:46.136
[ Scoffs 1

