17:41.144 --> 17:44.731
Well, hero robot
to protect Wayne.

17:44.856 --> 17:47.442
Help find him when he's lost.

17:48.986 --> 17:50.487
He's not lost, Vic.

17:51.947 --> 17:53.198
You found him.

17:55.409 --> 17:56.618
[ Bmws]

17:57.744 --> 17:59.621
Don't stay up too late.

18:02.374 --> 18:03.750
I won't.

18:05.002 --> 18:06.253
Love you.

18:06.378 --> 18:08.463
LOU:
Love you too.

18:08.589 --> 18:11.883
[ Pencil scratching ]

18:20.934 --> 18:24.271
[ Creak]

18:25.772 --> 18:27.274
[ Creak]

18:31.528 --> 18:33.614
[Thump]

18:53.842 --> 18:56.678
[ Door creaks ]

19:08.815 --> 19:10.609
[ Door creaks ]

19:20.702 --> 19:21.912
Wayne.

19:23.955 --> 19:26.083
Sugar for dinner is fun.

19:32.005 --> 19:34.132
Put that down
and come back to bed.

19:40.263 --> 19:41.890
I'm sorry.

19:42.015 --> 19:43.350
I'm so sorry, Morn.

19:43.475 --> 19:44.643
VIC:
It's okay.

19:48.480 --> 19:49.981
It's okay.

19:51.024 --> 19:52.818
You're alright.

20:06.915 --> 20:08.208
[ Sniffles ]

20:24.891 --> 20:26.601
.H6Y-
.H6Y-

