when you're done.

20:32.691 --> 20:33.692
Mm-hmm.

20:42.242 --> 20:43.118
Okay.

20:43.243 --> 20:44.911
You heard Dad.
Bed.

20:57.507 --> 20:59.426
Am I gonna be okay?

21:03.263 --> 21:05.307
Of course you are.
You're gonna be fine.

21:14.107 --> 21:15.525
Morn.

21:16.568 --> 21:17.861
VIC:
Yeah, baby?

21:18.987 --> 21:21.239
When Charlie Manx hurt you,

21:21.364 --> 21:23.408
did you get better?

21:24.743 --> 21:26.953
Like, all the way better?

21:32.459 --> 21:33.919
Yes.

21:34.044 --> 21:35.754
WAYNE:
Promise?

21:37.172 --> 21:39.299
I promise.

21:45.597 --> 21:47.265
Good night.
Sleep tight.

21:47.390 --> 21:48.892
I'll see you in the morning.

21:53.814 --> 21:56.024
Love you.

21:56.149 --> 21:57.526
[ Door closes ]

22:07.118 --> 22:08.537
[ Gasps]

22:10.831 --> 22:13.041
[ Door creaks ]

23:04.926 --> 23:06.094
[ Rabbit shrieks]

23:13.268 --> 23:14.352
Millie.

23:16.021 --> 23:18.773
Wayne McQueen.

23:21.526 --> 23:23.820
I want to go back
to Christmasland.

23:25.530 --> 23:26.948
Is there a way?

23:30.076 --> 23:32.329
I haven't found one.

23:32.454 --> 23:34.414
You're living here.

23:38.126 --> 23:39.336
So?

23:40.545 --> 23:42.005
WAYNE:
You look sad.

23:49.137 --> 23:50.972
It's not fair.

23:51.097 --> 23:54.017
