any Christmas at all.

23:55.143 --> 23:58.063
What was it like, living there?

24:04.527 --> 24:06.321
It was wonderful.

24:08.114 --> 24:10.825
I was boss of all the kids.

24:12.452 --> 24:15.080
I had all the candy
I could ever eat.

24:16.831 --> 24:19.250
I had anything I ever wanted.

24:20.543 --> 24:24.714
Here I have to sleep outside

24:24.839 --> 24:27.717
and hunt for food.

24:32.764 --> 24:35.433
