like me.

25:01.126 --> 25:04.004
Then someone might adopt you.

25:04.129 --> 25:08.383
But I'd be weak and ordinary.

25:14.764 --> 25:16.891
Do you want to grow up?

25:17.600 --> 25:18.685
No.

25:20.311 --> 25:23.481
But you could see
the Great Wall of China.

25:23.606 --> 25:27.277
